{"word":"G1334 - διηγέομαι - diēgéomai - dee-ayg-eh'-om-ahee - Declare","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διηγέομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diēgéomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-ayg-eh'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Declare</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சொல், அறிவி, விவரி, விவரஞ்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"to lead or carry a narration through to the end."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G2233 - ἡγέομαι - hēgéomai - hayg-eh'-om-ahee/2233\">G2233</a>; to <i>relate fully:</i> - declare, shew, tell.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}